{"tid":1593063,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"國慶日如廁徵文比賽","createTime":"2019-09-25T01:52:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T05:15:19.000Z","uid":99956,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3183c435d151676fa0dc39d64de75c63c3f47cc3","tid":1593063,"uid":99956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T01:52:25.000Z","msg":"今天不小心把心愛的屎痾了，事後我用了十五分鐘去細心欣賞，發現我那舊屎，竟然比起平日那個形態更美，然後我再用了十分鐘清潔屎忽，再為舊屎拍照。這短短的三十分鐘，算是今天我思緒最安穩的時間，被我痾掉的屎，是我今天看過最美好的東西，而那屎著落水面的那一聲，是聽過最美好的聲音，原來人生覺得最爛的事情，也未必是最糟，因為最糟的，可能一直就在眼前而未曾發現，又或者根本就是自己，我想我找到了答案<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JshNsMQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJshNsMQ.png&h=bddc806a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖片：杜汶澤喱騷"},{"pid":"dddccc08bd0a86daea87d31a40fcd62d7aaa97f7","tid":1593063,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T01:54:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚癲，香港冇大台運動，已經發展到929全球冇大台反支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592119</a>"},{"pid":"cd41f131591b457ce63cf425433412af1778d3d9","tid":1593063,"uid":99956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dddccc08bd0a86daea87d31a40fcd62d7aaa97f7","tid":1593063,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T01:54:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚癲，香港冇大台運動，已經發展到929全球冇大台反支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592119</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:15:19.000Z","msg":"929"}]}